<lb n="0293a07"/>
<lb n="0293a08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0293001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】明本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此經與麗本大異故別載之</note><title>佛說穰麌梨童女經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0293a09"/>
<lb n="0293a10"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0293002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唐〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0293002"><lem>唐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏沙門大廣智不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0293a11"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時薄伽梵。住舍衛國祇樹給
<lb n="0293a12"/>孤獨園。與大苾芻眾千二百五十人俱。復
<lb n="0293a13"/>有無量菩薩摩訶薩。及諸天龍藥叉乾闥
<lb n="0293a14"/>婆阿修羅迦樓羅緊那羅摩&CB00264;羅伽人非人
<lb n="0293a15"/>等皆來集會。爾時世尊告諸苾芻。我念往
<lb n="0293a16"/>昔。住雪山北遊香醉山。見一童女。百福相
<lb n="0293a17"/>好莊嚴其身。鹿皮為衣以諸毒蛇而為瓔
<lb n="0293a18"/>珞。將諸毒<note n="0293003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝蠱【宋】＊</note><app n="0293003"><lem>蟲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">蠱</rdg></app><note n="0293004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蚖蝮＝蟒蛇&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0293004"><lem>蚖蝮</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">蟒蛇</rdg></app>之類。前後圍繞常為
<lb n="0293a19"/>伴戲。飲<note n="0293005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（諸）＋毒&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0293005"><lem>毒</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">諸毒</rdg></app><note n="0293006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漿＋（及）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0293006"><lem>漿</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">漿及</rdg></app>食毒果。彼女見我謂言。仁
<lb n="0293a20"/>者當知聽我宣說穰麌<note n="0293007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梨＋（童女）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0293007"><lem>梨</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">梨童女</rdg></app>真<note n="0293008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（法）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0293008"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">言法</rdg></app>。能除世
<lb n="0293a21"/>間一切諸毒。若人聞此真言。及持我名者。
<lb n="0293a22"/>不被一切諸毒<note n="0293009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝傷&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0293009"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">傷</rdg></app>害。爾時童女為我宣說。
<lb n="0293a23"/>我從彼女聞已。常持此法饒益有情。我今
<lb n="0293a24"/>當說真言曰</p>
<lb n="0293a25"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去<note n="0293010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聲〕－【宋】【元】＊</note><app n="0293010"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>引</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>壹里蜜帝<note place="inline">引一</note>底<note place="inline">丁以
