<lb n="0293b18"/>普吒&CB00718;<note place="inline">&CB00353;簡<app type="＊" source="0293011"><lem>切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">反</rdg></app></note>拏囉&CB02092;<note place="inline">引九</note>薩跛囉&CB02092;<note place="inline">引十</note>薩跛
<lb n="0293b19"/>吒&CB00718;<note place="inline">准上音</note>拏囉&CB02092;<note place="inline">引十一</note>曩<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;囉&CB02092;<note place="inline">引十二</note>曩<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;
