<lb n="0293b21"/>&CB00256;尾曬<note place="inline">引十五</note>試<note place="inline">引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>試<note place="inline">引</note>多&CB00085;寧<note place="inline">引十六</note>滿跢<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0293b22"/>黎<note place="inline">引十七</note>伊<note place="inline">上</note>里黎<note place="inline">引十八</note>賀黎賀黎<note place="inline">十九</note>旦嬭<note place="inline">引</note>旦
<lb n="0293b23"/>嬭<note place="inline">引二十</note>怛&CB00600;<note place="inline">二十一</note>娑普<note place="inline">二合</note>吒娑普<note place="inline">二合</note>吒娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0293b24"/><note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引二十二</note></p>
<lb n="0293b25"/><p>爾時世尊說此陀羅尼已。告諸苾芻。我此
<lb n="0293b26"/>真言能解世間一切諸毒。<app type="＊" source="0293003"><lem>蟲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蠱</rdg></app>毒魅毒<note n="0293021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝蟲【元】</note><app n="0293021"><lem>蠱</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">蟲</rdg></app>
<lb n="0293b27"/>毒藥毒等不能為害。若有被毒中者。以此
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1264b.0293c" n="0293c"/>
<lb n="0293c01"/>真言加持皆得消滅。諸苾芻此穰麌梨陀
<lb n="0293c02"/>羅尼。於一切如來大會中說。真實不虛不
<lb n="0293c03"/>顛倒語。如語不異語諸有藥毒&CB00057;毒蟲毒
<lb n="0293c04"/>魅毒。欲來相害。能令&CB00230;著本所與者。令使
<lb n="0293c05"/>諸毒入水入火入柱入壁。亦令入地。所有
<lb n="0293c06"/>諸毒不令成毒。<note n="0293022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（若已毒者）＋悉【甲】</note><app n="0293022"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若已毒者悉</rdg></app>能除滅。若人受持此經
<lb n="0293c07"/>日誦一遍。非但滅世間諸毒。亦能除滅身
<lb n="0293c08"/>中三毒。爾時世尊。復說穰麌梨童女隨心
<lb n="0293c09"/>真言及成就法。修行者欲成就此法。先斷
<lb n="0293c10"/>五辛亦不食鹽不食油。斷語於一淨處。三
<lb n="0293c11"/>時澡浴三時換衣。結印誦隨心真言滿一
<lb n="0293c12"/>萬遍。則行法成就。<note n="0293023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝後【宋】【元】</note><app n="0293023"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>作一切事必獲成就
<lb n="0293c13"/>隨心真言曰</p>
<lb n="0293c14"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">上<app type="＊" source="0293010"><lem>聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>枲<note place="inline">思以<app type="＊" source="0293011"><lem>切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">反</rdg></app></note>爾<note n="0293024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（吠）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0293024"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">賀吠</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引一</note>戌<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00256;爾賀
<lb n="0293c15"/>吠<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0293025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（日）【甲】</note><app n="0293025"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;日</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0293026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臾＝曳【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0293026"><lem>臾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">曳</rdg></app><note place="inline">引三</note>仡囉<note place="inline"><note n="0293027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【甲】</note><app n="0293027"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>合</note>娑
<lb n="0293c16"/>仡囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑<note place="inline">四</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅<note place="inline">五</note>摩賀
<lb n="0293c17"/><note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>里<note place="inline">六</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>喻祇<note place="inline">霓夷<app type="＊" source="0293011"><lem>切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">反</rdg></app>引七</note>濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>里
<lb n="0293c18"/><note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引八</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>頗&CB00600;<note place="inline">引九</note>普吒囉奚<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0293c19"/>賀<note place="inline">引十</note>吽癹吒<note place="inline">上半聲</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十一</note></p>
<lb n="0293c20"/><p>我今復說穰虞梨印及觀行法。其根本印。
<lb n="0293c21"/>以二手相<note n="0293028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搏＝博【宋】【元】</note><app n="0293028"><lem>搏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">博</rdg></app>如掬物勢。以二小指相並。餘
<lb n="0293c22"/>八指各散開微曲即成。結此印誦前根本
<lb n="0293c23"/>真言。加持自身五處。所謂右肩左肩心喉
<lb n="0293c24"/>額等<note n="0293029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">項＝頂【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0293029"><lem>項</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">頂</rdg></app>上散印。次結隨心印。以右手五指
<lb n="0293c25"/>散開。微屈如師子爪形即成。結此印誦隨
<lb n="0293c26"/>心真言七遍加持五處。修行者作先行成
<lb n="0293c27"/>就法已。欲作法除毒之時。觀想自身為<note n="0293030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">穰＝讓【宋】【元】</note><app n="0293030"><lem>穰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">讓</rdg></app>
<lb n="0293c28"/>麌梨童女。身綠色狀如龍女。具足七頭項
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1264b.0294a" n="0294a"/>
<lb n="0294a01"/>有圓光。應想四臂。右第一手持三戟叉第
<lb n="0294a02"/>二手執三五莖孔雀尾。左第一手把一黑
<lb n="0294a03"/>蛇第二手施無畏。<note n="0294001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又＝叉【宋】</note><app n="0294001"><lem>又</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">叉</rdg></app>想七寶瓔珞耳璫環
<lb n="0294a04"/>釧。臂&CB00560;釧莊嚴其身。并以諸蛇用為瓔珞。
<lb n="0294a05"/>想從一一毛孔流出火焰。作此觀已於被
<lb n="0294a06"/>螫人前。結根本印及隨心印。加持自身五
<lb n="0294a07"/>處。取一熟銅&CB00179;盛水。誦隨心真言加持七
<lb n="0294a08"/>遍。以右手掬水打被螫人心上。所有毒氣
<lb n="0294a09"/>漸漸<note n="0294002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">銷＝消【宋】【元】＊</note><app n="0294002"><lem>銷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">消</rdg></app>除。即於真言句中增加此句。所
<lb n="0294a10"/>謂</p>
<lb n="0294a11"/><p type="dharani">左&CB00256;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>尾鑠<note place="inline">疏覺<app type="＊" source="0293011"><lem>切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">反</rdg></app></note>娑縛<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0294a12"/><p>即取淨土加持七遍。周匝圍繞被螫之人。
<lb n="0294a13"/>一切諸毒應時<app type="＊" source="0294002"><lem>銷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">消</rdg></app>滅。又法於被螫人前。結
<lb n="0294a14"/>本印數誦吽字一字真言。或誦撲字一字
<lb n="0294a15"/>真言加持。皆能除毒。若常受持此穰麌梨
<lb n="0294a16"/>法。能滅世間一切諸毒。所求無不遂心。爾
<lb n="0294a17"/>時世尊說此經已。時彼大會天龍藥叉人
<lb n="0294a18"/>非人等。聞佛所說皆大歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0294a19"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title>佛說穰麌梨童女<note n="0294003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0294003"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app><note n="0294004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書曰貞享四年中春十八一校了并點之淨嚴四十九載，元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教正德元年辛卯之秋十四日&CB00677;挍之性寂</note></title></jhead></juan></div1>
